She Can't Run Away From This Killer | Rebound | Full Suspense Horror Movie

Emotionally tormented after finding her boyfriend in bed with another woman, Claire decides to leave Los Angeles and drive back to her hometown of Chicago. She packs her bags and takes the long journey hoping to leave behind her current reality behind, only to find a new reality far worse.

2017.  Stars: Ashley James, Mark Scheibmeir, Wes O'Lee, Kevin Bulla, Julia Beth Stern
